nodes.text: Ve-Ta Naswee was a collector who gained prominence during the war between the First Order and the Resistance. Naswee was on a list of several wealthy clients of Dok-Ondar's Den of Antiquities, the store owned by fellow collector Dok-Ondar on the planet Batuu. Dok-Ondar prioritized his wealthy customers, taking their calls personally.
Ve-Ta Naswee was introduced in Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge: Traveler's Guide to Batuu, a 2020 reference book written by Cole Horton.
